chunks.html_content: This scheme is closed to new applicants.
chunks.plain_content:
Domestic Renewable Heat Incentive (RHI)
This scheme is closed to new applicants.

chunks.html_content:
You could get money towards renewable heating costs in your home.

You can claim for:

  • biomass boilers
  • solar water heating
  • certain heat pumps

Payments are made for 7 years and are based on the amount of renewable heat made by your heating system.

The money is paid through the Domestic RHI scheme.
chunks.plain_content:
Domestic Renewable Heat Incentive (RHI)
Types of heating
You could get money towards renewable heating costs in your home.
You can claim for:

  biomass boilers
  solar water heating
  certain heat pumps

Payments are made for 7 years and are based on the amount of renewable heat made by your heating system.
The money is paid through the Domestic RHI scheme.

chunks.html_content:
You can apply if you live in England, Scotland or Wales. You must either:

  • own your home
  • be a private or social landlord
chunks.plain_content:
Domestic Renewable Heat Incentive (RHI)
Eligibility
You can apply if you live in England, Scotland or Wales. You must either:

  own your home
  be a private or social landlord

chunks.html_content: New build properties will not normally be eligible. The only exception is if you’re building your own home.
chunks.plain_content:
Domestic Renewable Heat Incentive (RHI)
Eligibility
New build properties will not normally be eligible. The only exception is if you’re building your own home.
